			"description": [
				"\n                  <xhtml:p>Use the ASP.NET validation framework to check all program input before it is processed by the application. Example uses of the validation framework include checking to ensure that:</xhtml:p>\n                     <xhtml:ul>\n                        <xhtml:li>Phone number fields contain only valid characters in phone numbers</xhtml:li>\n                        <xhtml:li>Boolean values are only \"T\" or \"F\"</xhtml:li>\n                        <xhtml:li>Free-form strings are of a reasonable length and composition</xhtml:li>\n                     </xhtml:ul>\n               "
			]
		}
	],
